      "body" : "> Decimal() where possible, which does not round\r\n\r\nYou know this, but it is \"Decimal(str) where possible, which\r\ndoes not round, unlike Decimal(float)\"\r\n\r\nWhen Decimal(1) is fed a float, machine-specific witchcraft is\r\nhappening before the decimal module receives the data.\r\n",
